# Axodus Execution Authority Matrix

Current-state refresh: 2026-06-30 (`AXODUS-PORTFOLIO-REQ-01`)

This artifact must be read with the following accepted portfolio delta; older rows and recommendations are historical where they conflict:

- Academy: `L4_CONSOLIDATED` / `D3+` / `COMPLETE_NON_PRODUCTION`.
- Mining: `L4_CONSOLIDATED` / `D3+` / `COMPLETE_NON_PRODUCTION`.
- Defi: `L4_CONSOLIDATED_NON_PRODUCTION` / D-Level `UNASSESSED` / `GATED`; blockers remain open and `ADMIN_MUTATION` remains `UNSAFE`.
- ACS: `L4_READINESS` / `D3+` / `PAUSED`; not L4 Consolidated.
- Marketplace: `L4_CONSOLIDATED` / `D4` / `HOLD / BACKLOG_READY`; Phase 12A is not current priority.
- Next Best Move: `DOCUMENTATION-EPIC-01 - Publication Authority and Versioning Consolidation`.
- No production, execution, treasury, custody, wallet/signing, financial, provider, settlement, payout, billing or contract-write authority is added.

Date: 2026-06-30

Request: CROSS-REQ-04 - Governance & Execution Boundary Review

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This matrix is local/unversioned unless migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Matrix Summary

No reviewed nucleus currently has production execution authority. The matrix records current authority boundaries only.

| Nucleus | Governance Authority | Treasury Authority | Execution Authority | Production Authority | Approvals Required | Active Blockers |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Core | Can review architecture/governance packages; cannot execute governance | Can request/model limited impact; cannot approve/move funds | Architecture only; no product execution | NO | ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW, RC approval | Consumer pilot and RC evidence incomplete |
| Governance | Can prepare/review governance packages; proposal/vote/executor blocked | Can request treasury review; cannot move funds | Governance execution blocked | NO | GOVERNANCE_REVIEW, EXECUTION_REVIEW | Proposal, vote, DAO mutation and executor disabled |
| Documentation | Can review publication/governance-sensitive claims | NONE | NONE | NO | Publication authority, Business/Documentation review | Publication command and authority blocked |
| Dex | Can prepare DEX boundary package | Can model exposure; cannot move treasury | Read-only only; swaps/routing/liquidity blocked | NO | ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW, EXECUTION_REVIEW, TREASURY_REVIEW | DEX execution and treasury exposure blocked |
| Defi | Can prepare treasury/governance package | Planning/modeling only; movement blocked | Treasury/custody/staking blocked | NO | TREASURY_REVIEW, GOVERNANCE_REVIEW, EXECUTION_REVIEW | Custody, staking, treasury movement and implementation blocked |
| AxodusAPP | Can prepare UI/contract boundary package | Display only; no funds | Read-only shell only; wallet/signing blocked | NO | ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW, EXECUTION_REVIEW if wallet-adjacent | Wallet/trading/transaction flow blocked |
| Business | Can classify and create readiness packages | Can model readiness only; cannot approve/move funds | NON_EXECUTIVE | NO | BUSINESS_REVIEW plus owner escalation | Billing, treasury, ACS, governance and execution blocked |
| Marketplace | Can prepare settlement governance package | Settlement/payment modeling only | Settlement/payment/minting blocked | NO | TREASURY_REVIEW, GOVERNANCE_REVIEW, EXECUTION_REVIEW | Payments, settlement, minting, wallet blocked |
| Academy | Can prepare reward/certification governance package | Reward modeling only | Reward/certification/contract execution blocked | NO | GOVERNANCE_REVIEW, TREASURY_REVIEW | Rewards, certification issuance, contract writes blocked |
| Mining | Can prepare provider/payout governance package | Payout modeling only | Provider and payout execution blocked | NO | TREASURY_REVIEW, EXECUTION_REVIEW | Provider custody/execution and payouts blocked |
| ACS | Can prepare/review non-executive readiness and authority packages | NONE | Provisioning, autonomy, production permission/state mutation and runtime execution blocked | NO | EXECUTION_REVIEW, ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW, GOVERNANCE_REVIEW, SECURITY_REVIEW | Credentials, secrets, wallet/signing, providers, Hummingbot/runtime and mutation authority blocked |
| Trading | Can prepare credential/execution gate package | Exposure modeling only | Trading/exchange/withdrawal execution blocked | NO | EXECUTION_REVIEW, TREASURY_REVIEW, GOVERNANCE_REVIEW | Production credentials, exchange execution, withdrawals blocked |
| BBA-Agency | Can prepare claim/service package | Billing modeling only | Mock/local only; campaigns/CRM blocked | NO | BUSINESS_REVIEW, claim/compliance review | Billing, client execution, campaign dispatch blocked |
| Lottery | Can prepare compliance/randomness package | Prize/payout modeling only | Randomness/prize/payout/on-chain execution blocked | NO | EXECUTION_REVIEW, TREASURY_REVIEW, GOVERNANCE_REVIEW, compliance review | Compliance, VRF, prize, payout and launch blocked |

## Authority Counts

| Authority State | Count |
|---|---:|
| NON_EXECUTIVE or read-only/planning only | 6 |
| Execution-sensitive but blocked | 8 |
| Production authorized | 0 |
| Treasury movement authorized | 0 |
| Governance execution authorized | 0 |
| Wallet signing authorized | 0 |
| On-chain writes authorized | 0 |

## Approval Path Map

| Approval Path | Required For | Current Result |
|---|---|---|
| BUSINESS_REVIEW | Low/medium non-executive classification and readiness package creation | Allowed for planning only |
| ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW | Cross-nucleus contracts, UI consumption, persistence/API, provider and ownership transfers | Required before controlled integration |
| GOVERNANCE_REVIEW | DAO, governance plugin, proposal, vote, federation, constitutional or public authority scope | Required; execution still separately blocked |
| TREASURY_REVIEW | Funding, custody, settlement, revenue, billing, payout, debenture or treasury exposure | Required; movement remains blocked |
| EXECUTION_REVIEW | Wallet signing, on-chain writes, trading, DEX, settlement, payouts, ACS provisioning, production credentials | Required; no current authorization |
| PUBLICATION_AUTHORITY | Public docs publication, public claims, release workflow | Required; publication remains blocked |
| PRODUCTION_APPROVAL | Production services, external users, production DB/credentials/funds | Required; no current authorization |

## Boundary Statement

This matrix does not grant execution authority. It records that all production, treasury, wallet, settlement, payout, trading, DEX execution, ACS provisioning and on-chain authorities remain disabled or blocked.

