| Field | ACS Value |
|---|---|
| Current L-Level | `L4_CANDIDATE` |
| Recommended L-Level | `L4_READINESS` |
| D-Level | `D3+` |
| Production | `NON_PRODUCTION` |
| Execution | `EXECUTION_GATED` |
| Mutation authority | `NO_MUTATION_AUTHORITY` |
